value: 7997 - Membership Sports and Recreation Clubs Summary > CAZALYS CAIRNS LIMITED is an Australian public company. Its operations cover membership sports and recreation clubs. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. CAZALYS CAIRNS LIMITED is headquartered in Westcourt, Queensland. It is headed by director Reginald John Lillywhite. For the 2023 financial year, the company reported revenue of $33.79 million. Its net profit totalled $2.06 million. CAZALYS CAIRNS LIMITED forms part of the services industry sector.
